nodes.title: Workflow Information
widgets_values:
Improved Searge SDXL workflow for SDXL 1.0 - TEXT to IMAGE - created on Jul 27, 2023

To use this workflow, set up ComfyUI like this:

- Install the Searge SDXL custom node extension from https://github.com/SeargeDP/SeargeSDXL
  - open the command line in directory: ComfyUI/custom_nodes
  - run the command: git clone https://github.com/SeargeDP/SeargeSDXL.git
- Copy the SDXL 1.0 base model into ComfyUI/models/checkpoints
- Copy the SDXL 1.0 refiner model into ComfyUI/models/checkpoints
- Copy the SDXL 0.9 vae into ComfyUI/models/vae
- Copy the upscalers 4x-Ultrasharp.pth and 4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth into ComfyUI/models/upscale_models
- restart ComfyUI

Links:
SDXL 1.0 base:
 https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-diffusion-xl-base-1.0/resolve/main/sd_xl_base_1.0.safetensors
SDXL 1.0 refiner:
 https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-diffusion-xl-refiner-1.0/resolve/main/sd_xl_refiner_1.0.safetensors
SDXL 0.9 vae:
 https://huggingface.co/madebyollin/sdxl-vae-fp16-fix/resolve/main/sdxl_vae.safetensors
Download links for the upscalers are on:
 https://upscale.wiki/wiki/Model_Database
